{"tid":824250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[光速割席]范冰冰37歲生日 幾多圈中人留言祝賀？","createTime":"2018-09-17T04:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T04:03:38.000Z","uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7db637116861792948b09a1597a64f85f58f3a33","tid":824250,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T04:03:38.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】涉逃稅已神隱3個月的內地女星范冰冰今日（16日）37歲生日，她自6月事發後未有更新微博，今日被網民發現她終於「上線」，但沒有任何發文或點讚。范冰冰的版面因為出現在微博公版的生日動態上，不少網民在踏入零時即湧入該文給她留言祝福，但不到10多分鐘該文就被刪掉，她的帳戶則顯示「在線」，故有估計是她將這動態刪除，就連男友李晨也被發現連續上線5次，都不發一言。<br />\n<br />\n相比去年范冰冰生日，同時是男友李晨貼文公佈求婚成功，一眾圈中好友紛紛留言祝福，當時被笑指有近「半個娛圈」來簽到；今年范冰冰的生日就顯得冷清，幸有導演李玉雪中送炭，給范冰冰發文留言：「相識十二年，又到秋日時光，生日快樂！！」另外，有《紐約時報》記者指在日前中國外交部例行者會上，有記者問到范冰冰消失一事，發言人帶笑回應謂：「你覺得這是一個外交問題嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/F1SPeISEpQKZDi.NASAJUw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180916f115958.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FF1SPeISEpQKZDi.NASAJUw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20180916f115958.jpg&h=08774c6e&s={SIZE}\" />去年范冰冰生日兼公佈男友李晨求婚成功，獲近半個娛圈人祝賀。（微博圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/818737-%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82-%E8%8C%83%E5%86%B0%E5%86%B037%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%9F%E6%97%A5+%E5%B9%BE%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%88%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%BA%E7%95%99%E8%A8%80%E7%A5%9D%E8%B3%80%EF%BC%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F818737-%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582-%25E8%258C%2583%25E5%2586%25B0%25E5%2586%25B037%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2597%25A5%2B%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%259C%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2595%2599%25E8%25A8%2580%25E7%25A5%259D%25E8%25B3%2580%25EF%25BC%259F&d=qhK5bDgE7dGZbE5TZpbcsG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=fff5fb68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F818737-%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582-%25E8%258C%2583%25E5%2586%25B0%25E5%2586%25B037%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2597%25A5%2B%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%259C%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2595%2599%25E8%25A8%2580%25E7%25A5%259D%25E8%25B3%2580%25EF%25BC%259F&h=f0969dbd\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/818737-%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82-%E8%8C%83%E5%86%B0%E5%86%B037%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%9F%E6%97%A5+%E5%B9%BE%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%88%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%BA%E7%95%99%E8%A8%80%E7%A5%9D%E8%B3%80%EF%BC%9F</a>"}]}